		"description": "<p>You toss a handful of flower petals into the air, causing them to magically multiply and swirl around you in a 10-foot radius. While in this aura, you are considered to be benefiting from half cover. The aura moves with you and lasts until you lose concentration or dismiss it as a bonus action.</p>\n<p>Creatures entering the area of the swirling petals for the first time must make a Constitution saving throw versus your spell save DC or be blinded until the end of your next turn. Creatures who succeed on their saving throw versus this effect are immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.</p>",
